metadata.name: URBANA  01
metadata.description:
The collection is an ode to the beauty of the everyday, where the mundane is transformed into art through the Blockchain . Urban street elements such as graffiti walls, rusty fire escapes, and bustling intersections are just as much a part of the story as the women themselves, adding depth and texture to each image.

With each image, the viewer is transported into the heart of the city, able to feel the pulse of the streets and the energy of the women.
